Parīkṣā  (IE 8-3;<BR>EI 28, 31), same as Sanskrit Parīkṣaka; Sans kritised from Od8iyā Parichā; superintendent of a department or a governor;<BR>cf. Dvāra-parīkṣā.

परीक्षा
parīkṣā  (IA 10), same as divya, an ordeal. (CII 1), self-examination.

परीक्षक
Parīkṣaka  (IE 8-3), see Parīkṣā = Od8iyā Parichā.

