पार्श्विक
Pārśvika  (EI 9;<BR>CII 4), an aide-de-camp;<BR>also used to indicate a neighbour or one having land in the neighbourhood of the gift land (Ep. Ind., Vol. XXXIII, p. 197, text line 13).

पर्ताब्
partāb  (SII 1), Sanskrit pratāpa; a half pagoda.

पर्वमासोत्सव
parva-mās-otsava  (EI 15), a festival.

पारुत्थ
pāruttha,  a silver coin equal to 8 drammas of copper or billon (JNSI, Vol. XXII, p. 196).

