पट
paṭa, paṭā, pāṭa  (EI 28;<BR>Chamba), charter, deed;<BR>same as Sanskrit paṭṭa or paṭṭaka.

पाट
pāṭa,  cf. daṇḍapāṭa.

पातक
pātaka  (IE 8-1-2), ‘five’. Cf. pañca-mahāpātaka.

