व्याख्यावृत्ति
vyākhyā-vṛtti  (SITI), land set apart to meet the expenses of expounding the Purāṇas and other śāstras.

व्यक्त
vyakta  (CII 1), experienced.

व्यामिश्रभूमि
vyāmiśra-bhūmi  (IE 8-1), an area consisting of different kinds of land such as cultivated land, homestead land, fallow land, etc. See vyā-bhū.

व्यञ्जन
vyañjana,  cf. vē2ñjanam, viñjanam (SITI), condiment;<BR>vegetable relish;<BR>condiments and curry in food offerings;<BR>cf. vē2ñjana-bhaṇḍāram. (CII 1), a letter or an implication.

व्यापादित
vyāpādita  (LP), ‘much harassed’.

