yamalikāmbali  (HRS), a tax known from the Gāhaḍavāla records;<BR>also spelt yamalikamabali, yamalikāmali (q. v.).

यानक
yānaka  (Ep. Ind., Vol. IV, p. 253, note 4), probably a cart-road.

