Yaṣṭi-prātiṣṭhānaka  (ML), the erection of a pillar;<BR>same as Sanskrit yaṣṭi-pratiṣṭhāpana.

यथाकालभाविन्
yathākāla-bhāvin  (IE 8-3), same as vartamāna-bhaviṣyat, yathāsambadhyamānaka; also written as yathā-kāl-ādhyāsin (q. v.).

