yathā-sambadhyamānaka  (IA 9), same as yathākāla-bhāvin, vartamāna-bhaviṣyat, yathākāl-ādhyāsin.

यठि
yaṭhi  (CII 4), Prakrit;<BR>same as Sanskrit yaṣṭi (q. v.);<BR>a memorial pillar.

यति
Yati  (BL), a monk.

यात्रा
yātrā  (EI 11;<BR>CII 4), festival;<BR>the festival of a deity;<BR>same as yātr-otsava.

यात्रादान
yātrā-dāna  (EI 27), gift or levy for running a festival. (SITI), propitiatory gift made before starting on an expedition of conquest by the king.

यात्रोत्सव
yātr-otsava  (IE 8-5;<BR>EI 3, 9), same as yātrā (q. v.);<BR>the festival of a deity;<BR>festival in honour of a deity.

यौत
yauta  (CII 1), a respite;<BR>cf. yautaka.

